  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate cognition in patients with postural tachycardia
      syndrome (POTS) while lying down and standing and to assess the prevalence of hypermobile
      Ehlers-Danlos Syndrome in POTS.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
